      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This specimen is powered by the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual VANOS system for a linear 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise ZF 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been serviced to ensure long-term reliability. The chassis retains its factory-tuned MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, offering unparalleled steering feedback and lateral stability. The exterior paint depth is consistent across all panels, while the Nappa leather interior remains supple with no bolster wear or pixel degradation in the cluster. A turn-key masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
